  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-CON-03 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. This package was signed at the close of the primary review cycle; a supplementary mesh-refinement validation result was appended post-signing without triggering a re-signature, introducing a future-dated evidence item relative to the package signatureTimestamp.",
